---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="HederaCon 2025 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Denver, USA</div>
        <div class="event-title">HederaCon<br />2025</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Hedera hosted a 1-day conference adjacent to ETH Denver in February 2025 catering to the developer crowd followed by a closing party at Meow Wolf.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Hedera approached us to help them with a "relaunch" during ETH Denver. It was a one day, two-track conference held the day before ETH Denver began. We selected The Arch, a former brewery and warehouse that perfectly suited the needs of the event, and pushed the client outside of their comfort zone. It ended up being a perfect fit, and they were so happy with the outcome.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Staging</div>
            <p>Being the first large-scale conference for the team, we wanted to wow them while keeping it simple. Ultimately, we went with three LED screens for the main stage and 1 large LED board for the Developer Workshop. The main stage was a stunning LED board and stage that spanned the length of the room, creating a grand moment for their re-entry.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Closing Party</div>
            <p>The client was excited to secure Meow Wolf, and while the venue had been used many times before for parties, people lined up for hours to get in and stayed until the bitter end. It was the cherry on top of a successful partnership.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
